		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looks like PowerPaks are <a href="http://retrousb.com/index.php?productID=133" class="postlink">on sale</a> again!  The mapper files have been <a href="http://retrousb.com/downloads/POWERPAK111.zip" class="postlink">updated</a> again to fix battery RAM loading and saving (you can see in the <a href="http://retrousb.com/downloads/powerpakchanges.txt" class="postlink">changes file</a>).  I wonder when bunnyboy will post up an updated mapper development kit...

		

