		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nevermind, I figured it out.
<br />
<br />For some reason, PP.BIN (in the PLUGDONE dir), would get zeroed (empty file), when trying to load the plugin.
<br />
<br />I made it read only and that solved it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
